HEADWORD: Moebles
<hw>Moe"bles</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[OE., fr. OF.
<ets>moeble</ets>, <ets>mueble</ets>, movable, from L.
<ets>mobilis</ets>.]</ety> <def>Movables; furniture; -- also used in the
singular (<singw><it>moeble</it></singw>).</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <--
here we mark both the singular word and the written font -->
<rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
